
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
These are the CurrentYear/PreviousYear sales per Customer calculation I used : CY Sales per Customer, PY Sales per Customer |
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

===================================================

CY Sales per Customer

Formula

SUM([CY Sales]) / COUNTD([CY Customers])

===================================================

PY Sales per Customer

Formula

SUM([PY Sales ]) / COUNTD([PY Customers])

===================================================
